MVC Read me


Note:

1.config file inside config folder contains variables and function which is commonly used.
2.dbUtils or Utilities file contains database connection and runQuery functions.
3.View contains php and html files.
4.Controller contains logics and functions of model file and it is called by file in the view folder
5.Model folder contains file which is used to perform database queries and operations like select,insert,delete etc...
6.Inside model we create function which is called in controller file and function contains database queries.

php online platform : http://phpfiddle.org/